These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, analyst
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, horror
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, brazilian
2 different pets are kept: hamster, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, train
1. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
2. the analyst is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the owner of the hamster is the brazilian##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | tea       |
| Hobby         | baking   | rock-climbing     |
| Job           | software-developer | analyst   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | thriller  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | egyptian |
| Pet           | hamster      | goat     |
| Transport     | train    | bike   |

