.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, camping
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, nurse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, blues
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, indian
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, skateboard
1. the nurse is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the owner of the cat is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
4. the indian is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | lemonade    | coffee |
| Hobby         | camping        | photography  |
| Job           | accountant | nurse  |
| Music-Genre   | blues            | d&b    |
| Nationality   | pakistani     | indian   |
| Pet           | guinea-pig         | cat    |
| Transport     | ship           | skateboard      |

